### 8. Data (`data/raw/`)

20 Markdown files representing 4 corporate capital events (2018, 2019, 2021, 2024):

```
SH7_Event{N}_{YEAR}.md         — Form SH-7
BoardMeeting_Event{N}_{YEAR}.md — Board resolution
EGM_Event{N}_{YEAR}.md         — EGM resolution
Notice_of_EGM_{YEAR}.md        — EGM notice (classified but not extracted)
MOA_Event{N}_{YEAR}.md         — Memorandum of Association Clause V
```

